      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Candidate A has a polished, professional tone, using formal language that suggests they understand corporate expectations. Candidate B sounds overly casual and unprofessional, using slang and informal phrasing that would likely be inappropriate for serious client interactions. For a client-facing role, Candidate A demonstrates a much more suitable and mature communication style.",
